<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>Profile Viewed Notification</title>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
</head>

<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; min-width: 100%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; background-color: #FAFAFA; color: #222222;">
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <div style="background-color: #0070f3; padding: 24px; color: #ffffff;">
            <h1 style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.25; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: center;">
                Your Profile Has Been Viewed!</h1>
        </div>
        <div style="padding: 24px; background-color: #ffffff;">
            <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 24px;">Hello {{candidateName}},</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 24px;">We wanted to let you know that a recruiter has viewed your profile. Here are the details:</p>
            
            <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 24px;">
                <img src="{{employerAvatar}}" alt="Recruiter Avatar" style="width: 50px; height: 50px; border-radius: 50%; margin-right: 16px;">
                <div>
                    <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 600;">Recruiter: {{employerName}}</p>
                    <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">Company: {{companyName}}</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 24px;">If you're interested in this recruiter or want to explore potential opportunities, don't hesitate to reach out!</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 24px;">We hope you get the opportunity you're looking for!</p>
        </div>
        <div style="background-color: #f6f6f6; padding: 24px;">
            <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 24px;">
                If you have any questions, please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@dennis.com" style="color: #000; text-decoration: none;">support@dennis.com</a>.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
